metadata.description: Performance comparison across different microservice systems
metadata.note: We primarily use TrainTicket for main experiments

TrainTicket.description: 41-service train ticket booking system (our main benchmark)
TrainTicket.why_challenging: Large service count, complex dependencies, realistic e-commerce patterns

SockShop.why_easier: Fewer services (smaller search space), simpler dependency graph

analysis.note: Performance decreases as service count increases (harder search space)
analysis.scalability: System maintains 76%+ AC@1 even on 41-service system (excellent)
analysis.generalization: Consistent performance across different architectural patterns
